<plot>Anthony Leone is a successful Writer/Director of the Movie "Goomba Goons" and the Studio that made this happen wants him to Direct "Goomba Goons II". Anthony does not want to be stuck with the Mobster stereotype and instead wants to make a small movie with big heart about Italian families in Brooklyn and his Grandpa's Pizzaria. The studio head changes his mind and says yes to Anthony's Little Brooklyn movie after eating Anthony's Dad's (Carmine Leone) Cheesecake.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501490</url></doc>
